==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tenpenny
<hw>Ten"pen*ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Valued or sold at
ten pence; <as>as, a <ex>tenpenny</ex> cake</as>. See 2d <er>Penny</er>,
<pos>n.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tenpenny</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tenpenny
<hw>Ten"pen*ny</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Denoting a size of nails. See
1st <er>Penny</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tenpins</ent>⟦br⟧
